Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.42,Arial black,,0,0,0,,Strajk !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.19,Arial black,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC778BB&}Takže aj on má konečný nadhod !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.43,Arial black,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC778BB&}No, jednoznačne je dobrý nahadzovač...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.23,Arial black,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC778BB&}Ale nabudúce trafím !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.30,Arial black,,0,0,0,,A-Abe-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.70,Arial black,,0,0,0,,T-Tu to máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.87,Arial black,,0,0,0,,Oh, ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:45.74,Arial black,,0,0,0,,Pomôžem ti to dať na nohy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:51.38,Arial black,,0,0,0,,Hej
